# 014 — UX shell I: schematic view, repeat builder, templates, drag-drop & comparison workspace (Part J §J.1–J.5)

## Spec reference

- `C:\GitHub\Berreman\specs\0022\.spec-md` — parent spec (Spec 0022, Berreman Optical Constructor — solution architecture & cross-cutting contract).
- Slice 001 (`.slices/001.slice-md`) — scaffold + the buildable FuncUI interpretation every UI-touching slice relies on.
